snippet.title: Only In Darkness Trailer
snippet.description:
Itch link: https://spalato-bros.itch.io/only-in-darkness

Starting off as a student project, Only In Darkness is an FPS horror game, where you move in the light and it moves in the dark...

Publishing on the 29th of October 2019.
